00:04:43,328 --> 00:04:46,991
Gde si bio do sad, momce?
Autobus polazi za 15 minuta.

3
00:04:47,099 --> 00:04:49,294
Do farme.
Morao sam ovo da se vratim po ovo.

4
00:04:49,401 --> 00:04:51,528
Treba mi nesto za citanje.

5
00:04:51,637 --> 00:04:54,105
U svakom slucaju, ja sam, uh...
Ja sam sve spremio gore.

6
00:04:54,206 --> 00:04:56,640
Tvoja majka je gore.
O cemu je knjiga?

7
00:04:56,742 --> 00:04:59,336
- Oh, Dejvid Koperfild.
- Bices srecan ako budes imao vremena za citanje.

8
00:04:59,444 --> 00:05:01,344
Ja nikada nisam imao.

9
00:05:02,514 --> 00:05:05,176
- Je li sve poneo?
- Naravno, i ne treba mu puno.

10
00:05:05,284 --> 00:05:08,276
- Sta si mislio time, "i ne treba mu puno"?
- Pa, oni ce mu dati sve sto treba-

11
00:05:08,387 --> 00:05:10,287
odecu, namirnice, i tako to.

12
00:05:10,389 --> 00:05:12,755
Njemu treba ono sto sam mu ja dala.

13
00:05:12,858 --> 00:05:16,055
Vreme je za autobus, momce.
Ne zelis da propustis taj voz.

14
00:05:23,402 --> 00:05:26,462
- Cao, Mama.
- Srecno, Sine.

15
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:11,038
Podjimo.

16
00:07:14,279 --> 00:07:17,806
Pomeri se, sine.
Povuci se. Povuci se.

17
00:07:17,916 --> 00:07:21,044
- Iznesite! Iznesite!
- Naslonite na zid.

18
00:08:04,729 --> 00:08:06,720
Ima nekoga gore.

19
00:08:18,310 --> 00:08:21,746
- Idemo.
- Povucite ta creva! Nazad! Nazad!

20
00:08:21,847 --> 00:08:25,112
U redu, cuvajte se!
Rusi se! Rusi se!

21
00:08:35,660 --> 00:08:38,527
Zao mi je, momce. Upravo si ga propustio.

22
00:08:57,215 --> 00:09:00,082
Idi i naspavaj se malo.
Ja cu zavrsiti ovde.

23
00:09:25,677 --> 00:09:29,044
Okupili smo se ovde,
draga i voljena braco po Hristu...

24
00:09:29,147 --> 00:09:31,342
da ovo dete bude ponovo rodjeno...

25
00:09:31,449 --> 00:09:34,816
i primljeno u porodicu
Hristove crkve...

26
00:09:34,920 --> 00:09:38,583
zahvalimo svemogucem Bogu
za ove blagodeti...

27
00:09:38,690 --> 00:09:42,626
i da, svi zajedno,
pomolimo se Bogu za njega...

28
00:09:42,727 --> 00:09:46,288
da ovo dete do kraja svog zivota bude
prosvetljno prema ovom novom pocetku.

29
00:10:04,683 --> 00:10:08,813
Jesi li ti za kamp?
Hej, ti!

30
00:10:08,920 --> 00:10:12,253
- Jesi li ti za kamp?
- Jesam.

31
00:10:12,357 --> 00:10:15,656
Malo si zakasnio, sinko.
Ostali su stigli sinoc.

32
00:10:15,760 --> 00:10:17,421
Znam.

33
00:10:17,529 --> 00:10:19,690
Uhvatilo te bombardovanje, eh?

34
00:10:19,798 --> 00:10:21,823
- Da.
- Oh, pa, nema veze, sinko.

35
00:10:21,933 --> 00:10:26,165
Moraces da pesacis.
Nema puno milja.

36
00:11:26,498 --> 00:11:29,194
Spusti kofer dole.

37
00:11:29,300 --> 00:11:31,598
- Ime?
- Tomas Bedous.

38
00:11:31,703 --> 00:11:33,330
Gospodine.

39
00:11:33,438 --> 00:11:35,929
- Tomas Bedous, gospodine.
- Kasnis.

40
00:11:38,810 --> 00:11:41,802
I... stoj!

41
00:11:49,688 --> 00:11:52,714
I... stoj!

42
00:11:56,428 --> 00:11:58,328
Ko si ti?

43
00:11:59,531 --> 00:12:02,796
- Tomas Bedous, gospodine.
- Da li ti licim na oficira?

44
00:12:02,901 --> 00:12:04,869
- Napred, mars!
- Ne, gospodine.

45
00:12:04,969 --> 00:12:07,597
Ne zovi me "gospodine" onda.

46
00:12:07,706 --> 00:12:10,266
Ko ti je dozvolio da upadnes ovde?

47
00:12:10,375 --> 00:12:12,343
- Da sta?
- Da udjes ovde.

48
00:12:12,444 --> 00:12:15,470
Da udjes u sobu.
Da otvoris vrata i da izvedes ulazak.

49
00:12:16,881 --> 00:12:20,009
- Niko.
- Uradi to onda kako treba.

50
00:12:20,118 --> 00:12:22,678
Izadji napolje, kucaj.

51
00:12:22,787 --> 00:12:25,779
I kad ja kazem "da,"
udji i kazi, "Trazim dozvolu za ulaz."

52
00:12:27,425 --> 00:12:29,552
Hajde.

53
00:12:34,299 --> 00:12:36,824
Bedous.

54
00:12:36,935 --> 00:12:39,597
Tvoj kofer... uzmi ga.

55
00:12:53,051 --> 00:12:54,951
Da?

56
00:12:58,757 --> 00:13:02,454
- Ko si ti?
- Bedous. Trazim dozvolu za ulaz.

57
00:13:02,560 --> 00:13:05,358
Udji, Redove Bedous.

58
00:13:05,463 --> 00:13:08,330
Mozes uzeti onaj.

59
00:13:17,575 --> 00:13:19,475
Ostavi to.

60
00:13:19,577 --> 00:13:22,944
Vec dovoljno kasnis.
Sledece po redu je sisanje.

61
00:13:23,047 --> 00:13:26,175
Naci ces berbernicu
odmah pored kancelarije cete.

62
00:13:26,284 --> 00:13:28,752
- Sledeci!
- Stani mirno. Stani mirno.

63
00:13:28,853 --> 00:13:31,447
Stani mirno.. Sledeci.

64
00:13:31,556 --> 00:13:33,922
Sledeci. Ime?

65
00:13:34,025 --> 00:13:36,050
- Bedous, gospodine.
- Malo si mrsav, zar ne?

66
00:13:36,161 --> 00:13:38,061
Da, gospodine.

67
00:13:39,197 --> 00:13:41,097
- Imas li kasalj?
- Ne, gospodine.

68
00:13:41,199 --> 00:13:43,724
- U redu. Obuci se tamo.
- Sledeci.

69
00:13:46,638 --> 00:13:49,505
- Hocete li me ubosti time?
- Ruku, molim.

70
00:13:55,947 --> 00:13:58,814
Osecas li se bolje?

71
00:13:58,917 --> 00:14:01,112
Ne volim igle.

72
00:14:01,219 --> 00:14:04,655
Je li to sve?
Ja ne volim celu smrdljivu vojsku.

73
00:14:04,756 --> 00:14:08,783
Svi regruti, poredjajte se pored vrata.
Postrojite se. Pokret!

74
00:14:08,893 --> 00:14:12,090
Dobro!
Abrahams, Arlot, Bedous!

75
00:14:12,197 --> 00:14:15,496
Malkolm, Partridz Silver, Jang.

76
00:14:15,600 --> 00:14:17,932
Dobro. Da vas vidim.

77
00:14:33,084 --> 00:14:35,416
Mozes li mi reci sta imas tu?

78
00:14:36,921 --> 00:14:40,220
Jedan par gaca, P.T.
Jedan par gaca, kruzne.

79
00:14:40,325 --> 00:14:42,919
Jedna balaklava.
Jedan par tregera. Jedan par cizama.

80
00:14:43,027 --> 00:14:45,154
Veliki kaput, carape, prsluci, dokolenice.

81
00:14:45,263 --> 00:14:47,595
Tvrda tkanina,
malo i veliko pakovanje.

82
00:14:47,699 --> 00:14:49,599
Ratnicka odora, gas maska.

83
00:14:51,202 --> 00:14:54,638
Porcija, cutura,
noz, viljuska i kasika.

84
00:14:56,040 --> 00:14:58,600
Nesto jos osim toga?

85
00:14:58,710 --> 00:15:00,678
Mislim da ne.

86
00:15:02,780 --> 00:15:04,805
Sta je to?

87
00:15:04,916 --> 00:15:06,907
To je kanap za ciscenje puske.

88
00:15:07,018 --> 00:15:08,918
Ucis.

89
00:15:11,155 --> 00:15:13,055
U redu, svi vi!

90
00:15:13,157 --> 00:15:16,593
Ima da odrzavate ovaj pod tako blistavim
da me zaslepi, i ima da pocnete upravo sad!

91
00:15:16,694 --> 00:15:19,288
Hajde da odmah rascistimo dve stvari!

92
00:15:19,397 --> 00:15:23,857
Prva stvar:
Komanda, "Voljno."

93
00:15:23,968 --> 00:15:26,596
Necete se pokretati ni malo...

94
00:15:26,704 --> 00:15:29,298
dok ne izgovorim tu komandu!

95
00:15:29,407 --> 00:15:33,173
Necete se vrpoljiti,
okretati ili bilo sta drugo!

96
00:15:33,278 --> 00:15:35,246
- Je li to jasno?
- Da, kaplare!

97
00:15:35,346 --> 00:15:37,780
- Je li to jasno??
- Da, kaplare!

98
00:15:39,083 --> 00:15:42,610
Ustaj! Umivanje! Brijanje! Oblaci se!

99
00:15:42,720 --> 00:15:44,779
Ocistite ovu sobu u baraci,
i to hocu tako da sija!

100
00:15:44,889 --> 00:15:47,050
- Jedan!
- Dva!
- Tri!

101
00:15:47,158 --> 00:15:48,819
- Cetiri!
- Pet!
- Sest!

102
00:15:48,927 --> 00:15:50,554
- Sedam!
- Osam!
- Devet!

103
00:15:50,662 --> 00:15:52,186
- Deset!
- Jedanaest!
- Dvanaest!

104
00:15:52,297 --> 00:15:56,393
Neparni brojevi, jedan korak napred!

105
00:15:56,501 --> 00:16:00,995
Parni brojevi, jedan korak nazad!

106
00:16:01,105 --> 00:16:03,005
- Mars!
- Jedan, dva!

107
00:16:03,107 --> 00:16:05,371
- Jang, koliko ceta ima u jednom bataljonu?
- Cetiri cete.

108
00:16:05,476 --> 00:16:09,003
- Bedous, ime bataljonskog narednika.
- Bataljonski narednik Palmer.

109
00:16:09,113 --> 00:16:12,571
- Tacno! Ima li pitanja?
- Bataljon je osnovan 1685.

110
00:16:13,618 --> 00:16:15,643
- Da.
- Zbog cega?

111
00:16:17,255 --> 00:16:19,553
Mislim, da li je bilo nekog posebnog razloga?

112
00:16:19,657 --> 00:16:21,852
- Sta ti mislis?
- Ne znam.

113
00:16:21,960 --> 00:16:24,360
Da zadivi Francuze!

114
00:16:25,463 --> 00:16:28,296
U redu. Da pogledamo sta ste uradili
do sada. Stanite pored svojih kreveta!

115
00:16:45,550 --> 00:16:48,178
Dobro! Sada, pocecemo sve
iz pocetka, hocemo li?

116
00:16:48,286 --> 00:16:50,379
- Broji!
- Jedan, dva, tri! Jedan!

117
00:16:50,488 --> 00:16:53,321
Ne mrdaj! Savrseno ne mrdaj!

118
00:16:53,424 --> 00:16:56,587
Formiraj liniju po tri! Brzo.

119
00:16:56,694 --> 00:16:58,662
Mars! Centar. Pozadi.

120
00:16:58,763 --> 00:17:01,061
Ispred. Centar. Pozadi.

121
00:17:01,165 --> 00:17:03,360
Ispred. Centar. Pozadi.

122
00:17:03,468 --> 00:17:05,663
Ispred. Centar. Pozadi.

123
00:17:05,770 --> 00:17:07,897
Ispred. Centar. Pozadi.

124
00:17:08,006 --> 00:17:10,873
Ispred. Pozadi. I popuni tu.

125
00:17:12,243 --> 00:17:14,143
Dobro!

126
00:17:14,245 --> 00:17:16,145
- Okret!
- Jedan, dva...

127
00:17:16,247 --> 00:17:18,442
Sada se razmaknite! Hajde, brze!

128
00:17:18,549 --> 00:17:22,178
U visini ruku, tvoje desno!
Pogled na desno!

129
00:17:22,286 --> 00:17:24,550
Dizi ruku.

130
00:17:24,655 --> 00:17:27,749
... napred!

131
00:17:35,600 --> 00:17:38,569
- Bedous, zar ne?
- Da, gospodine.

132
00:17:38,669 --> 00:17:41,035
Sta nisi dobro uradio, Bedous?

133
00:17:43,674 --> 00:17:46,643
Izgleda da sam propustio da izbelim
pojas ispod kopce, gospodine.

134
00:17:46,744 --> 00:17:49,542
- Sredi to sledeci put.
- Da, gospodine.

135
00:17:49,647 --> 00:17:52,616
Na desno! Brzo marsiranje!

136
00:17:52,717 --> 00:17:56,084
Leva, desna! Leva, desna! Sad!

137
00:17:56,187 --> 00:17:58,087
Odred!

138
00:17:59,357 --> 00:18:01,257
- Stoj!
- Leva, jedan, dva!

139
00:18:01,359 --> 00:18:04,556
Sta to, dodjavola, radis, Bedous?
Pomeri se jako nazad!

140
00:18:07,331 --> 00:18:10,095
Uvrci! Uvrci!

141
00:18:10,201 --> 00:18:11,828
Pocepaj ga!

142
00:18:18,876 --> 00:18:22,073
Hajde! Hajde! Drzite ruke gore!

143
00:18:22,180 --> 00:18:25,081
- Jebem mu, prodji izmedju--
- Vhoa!

144
00:18:25,183 --> 00:18:28,778
Ne gledaj dole. Ne gledaj dole!
Prokleta budalo!

145
00:18:28,886 --> 00:18:32,788
Hajde! Hajde!
Plasite se da ne pokvasite noge?

146
00:18:34,592 --> 00:18:38,119
Pazite da vam te puske ostanu suve!

147
00:18:38,229 --> 00:18:41,027
Penji se uz te proklete merdevine!

148
00:18:44,769 --> 00:18:48,227
Hajde! Sta mislis da je ovo, izlet?

149
00:18:50,074 --> 00:18:52,634
Hajde!
Ustaj, ti blesavi stvore!

150
00:18:56,447 --> 00:18:59,507
Hajde! Jos niste zavrsili!

151
00:19:16,033 --> 00:19:17,933
Jebem ti. Moram da zapalim.

152
00:19:18,970 --> 00:19:20,870
Oni su ispred.

153
00:19:20,972 --> 00:19:23,998
Pa, ti produzi.
Ja cu da zastanem da zapalim.

154
00:19:44,162 --> 00:19:47,154
- Mrzim ovaj rat.
- Preboleces.

155
00:19:50,001 --> 00:19:53,596
Ne, nije to u pitanju.
Moja devojka.

156
00:19:55,206 --> 00:19:57,436
Verili smo se, znas, i onda...

157
00:19:59,210 --> 00:20:02,338
i kada su me mobilisali,
pa...

158
00:20:02,446 --> 00:20:04,414
njen stari mi nije
dozvolio da je ozenim.

159
00:20:05,683 --> 00:20:07,878
Nek ide bestraga.

160
00:20:07,985 --> 00:20:11,352
Rekao je da treba da
sacekamo dok ne dobijemo rat.

161
00:20:11,455 --> 00:20:13,355
Kopile.

162
00:20:14,792 --> 00:20:18,922
Dozvolio bi da mu Svabe tucaju zenu
cim bi mu pokucali na vrata.

163
00:20:30,875 --> 00:20:32,843
Zeleo sam da letim.

164
00:20:34,745 --> 00:20:36,645
Nisam prosao lekarski.

165
00:20:38,216 --> 00:20:40,116
Nisam znao za to.

166
00:20:43,888 --> 00:20:46,857
- Ko tebe ceka kod kuce, Tomi?
- Koga ja imam?

167
00:20:48,726 --> 00:20:51,559
Pa, tu su mama i tata, predpostavljam.

168
00:20:51,662 --> 00:20:53,630
I Tina.

169
00:20:54,899 --> 00:20:56,867
Dobro za tebe, druze.

170
00:20:56,968 --> 00:20:58,868
Pusti me da pogadjam.

171
00:20:58,970 --> 00:21:02,337
Ona ima smedju kosu, braon oci...

172
00:21:02,440 --> 00:21:05,273
belu kozu, lepe sise, tacno?

173
00:21:06,911 --> 00:21:08,879
Tina je koker spanijel.

174
00:21:11,816 --> 00:21:14,341
- Ona je divan pas.
- Kucka?

175
00:21:14,452 --> 00:21:16,977
Da. Kucka.

176
00:21:27,164 --> 00:21:29,792
Sta ces raditi kada se sve ovo zavrsi?

177
00:21:32,103 --> 00:21:34,003
Oh, ne znam.

178
00:21:35,840 --> 00:21:37,740
Ja imam planove.

179
00:21:38,809 --> 00:21:40,709
Garaza, druze.

180
00:21:40,811 --> 00:21:44,474
Kupicu garazu negde ovde u blizini
u bacicu se na posao secenja metala.

181
00:21:44,582 --> 00:21:47,278
- Sta kazes na to da se udruzis sa mnom, Tom?
- Hej. Trebalo bi da krenemo.

182
00:21:54,692 --> 00:21:56,887
Izlazis sutra sa mnom i sa momcima?

183
00:21:56,994 --> 00:21:59,861
Proslavljamo... kraj obuke.

184
00:21:59,964 --> 00:22:03,661
Pab je pun poslepodne,
uvece je prava ludnica.

185
00:22:03,768 --> 00:22:05,736
Dobro. Dobro. vazi.

186
00:22:07,471 --> 00:22:09,405
O cemu je film?

187
00:22:09,507 --> 00:22:12,965
Zaboravi slike, druze.
U pitanju je zena.

188
00:22:13,077 --> 00:22:17,377
Sesces pored dobrog komada u poslednjim redovima,
i otici cete pre nego sto se i pojavi naslov filma.

189
00:22:19,417 --> 00:22:21,510
Oh, za Bozje zdravlje.

190
00:22:22,620 --> 00:22:25,714
- Imaju bar 10 minuta prednosti.
- Mislis?

191
00:22:25,823 --> 00:22:28,018
Nema prokletog provoda za nas veceras.

192
00:22:30,628 --> 00:22:33,256
- Idem dole.
- Sta, dole nizbrdo?

193
00:22:33,364 --> 00:22:34,991
Da.

194
00:22:35,099 --> 00:22:38,034
Hej! Nemoj to da radis.
Ubices se.

195
00:23:06,364 --> 00:23:10,733
- Da li ga je pregledao vojni lekar.?
- Vojni lekar je rekao da nema potrebe za lecenjem, gospodine.

196
00:23:10,835 --> 00:23:12,769
Zatvorenik i pratnja...

197
00:23:12,870 --> 00:23:15,964
i... okret!

198
00:23:17,942 --> 00:23:20,968
Zatvorenik i pratnja, brzi mars!

199
00:23:21,078 --> 00:23:23,638
Leva, desna! Leva, desna!

200
00:23:23,748 --> 00:23:25,716
Zatvorenik i pratnja, stoj!

201
00:24:41,292 --> 00:24:43,487
Redove Bedous, ulazi!

202
00:24:48,466 --> 00:24:51,924
U 0900 casova, vi cete paradno
proci kroz glavnu kapiju...

203
00:24:52,036 --> 00:24:55,005
gde cete sacekati transport
koji ce vas odvesti u vase jedinice.

204
00:24:55,105 --> 00:24:57,232
Vraticete se ovde do 2100 sati...

205
00:24:57,341 --> 00:25:00,606
ili vas rodjena majka nece prepoznati
kad ja budem zavrsio sa vama.

206
00:25:00,711 --> 00:25:03,271
Zaboravite sve sto sam vam rekao
i nece vas biti u blizini...

207
00:25:03,380 --> 00:25:06,178
- Utesno, zar ne?
- ...da mi napisete pismo zahvalnosti
kada se rat bude zavrsio.

208
00:25:06,283 --> 00:25:09,081
Saljes signale, Bedous?

209
00:25:09,186 --> 00:25:11,347
Samo za "pobedu," kaplare.

210
00:25:15,092 --> 00:25:16,992
Ovo je Muviton.

211
00:32:25,222 --> 00:32:27,156
Lezi dole tamo! Lezi dole!

212
00:33:14,304 --> 00:33:16,864
- Zdravo, Dzek.
- Sve moramo sami, zar ne?

213
00:33:23,880 --> 00:33:26,041
Ti si usamljenicka vrsta
cudaka, zar ne?

