sa mnom, molim te?

278
00:41:47,584 --> 00:41:51,418
- Nemam nista protiv.
- Hajdemo onda.

279
00:42:12,342 --> 00:42:14,902
- Kako ide, Arture?
- Dobro.

280
00:42:15,011 --> 00:42:16,979
- Pazi.
- Zao mi je.

281
00:42:18,581 --> 00:42:21,573
