onima koji su sve ovo prvi poceli.

304
00:44:20,336 --> 00:44:22,304
Da.

305
00:44:35,084 --> 00:44:36,984
Mislim da si zaista divna.

306
00:44:37,086 --> 00:44:38,917
Stvarno?

307
00:44:41,157 --> 00:44:43,216
Da, mislim.

308
00:44:43,326 --> 00:44:45,191
I ti se meni svidjas.

309
00:44:48,798 --> 00:44:50,766
Osecam se mnogo bolje sad.

310
00:44:51,801 --> 00:44:53,598
Bio sam bas...

